message: fixed cursor position and first character deletion on masks with non-permanent first character
use Karma with PhantomJS for tests
legacy update (get rid of createClass, setProps, string ref, etc.)
use mocha and chai for all tests
remove babel options from npm build script
broken commonjs module path in package.json
dev for IE8 (requires React 0.14 for that)
Fix IE8 support in npm run dev

Combine npm scripts into rollup multiconfig

In this diff I combined rollup configs to reduce node and rollup load
time. It is saved half of build time (7-8s to 3.5s for me).

Added size snapshot plugin to track the size across any commit. This
increased a bit build time to ~5s. So we still win here.

Removed `replace` plugin which does not affect existing code.

Reused `main` field from package.json in rollup config.

Refactor babel config

Replaced `es2015` preset (which is deprecated) with `env`

Renamed `tests` env to `test` as more widely used and considered as
default in some tools (for example jest).

Added commonjs babel plugin to not treat it as loose. Modules should be
handled as strict as possible.

Upgraded to stage-3 since stage-2 features are not used.
Allow to pass input components as children
Run linter on pre-commit only against staged files

Version 3.0.0-alpha.2

3.0.0-alpha.1 was mistakengly tagged as latest and unpublished
